Editor’s note: This livestream has ended. You may wacth the recording above. JOHANNESBURG – MultiChoice and SuperSport have responded to the incident that took place in its studios on Saturday. Former rugby player, Ashwin Willemse, walked out following a fall-out with colleagues Naas Botha and Nick Mallet. SuperSport CEO, Gideon Kobane, says they’ll continue engaging the parties involved. "This has become a national issue. We take this incident with a seriousness it deserves….we don’t want to rush for the sake of convenience,” said Kobane. eNCA